OL,3,CHuge rise in passengers smuggling
OL,4,Ccannabis in luggage at UK airports
OL,6,FSo far this year, 378 suspects have
OL,7,Fbeen detained compared to 136 suspects
OL,8,Fin 2023 with the National Crime Agency
OL,9,Fblaming countries where the drug is
OL,10,Flegalised.
OL,12,FThe amount of cannabis found in
OL,13,Fsuitcases at UK airports has tripled
OL,14,Fin under a year, officials report.
OL,16,FIn 2024, about 15 tonnes of cannabis
OL,17,Fhave been seized at airports, compared
OL,18,Fto five tonnes throughout the whole of
OL,19,F2023, and two tonnes in 2022.
