OL,6,FA total of 136 suspects were arrested
OL,7,Fin 2023, while 378 have been detained
OL,8,Fso far this year.
OL,10,FOfficials at the National Crime Agency
OL,11,F(NCA) say overproduction of the drug
OL,12,Fin countries where it has been
OL,13,Flegalised, and the chance of bigger
OL,14,Fprofits in the UK market, might be
OL,15,Fbehind the increase.
OL,17,FPassengers are being caught with large
OL,18,Fquantities of cannabis in their
OL,19,Fluggage.
