OL,3,CHuge rise in passengers smuggling
OL,4,Ccannabis in luggage at UK airports
OL,6,FRecent cases include 51-year-old
OL,7,FSpanish national Fernando Mayans
OL,8,FFuster, who was stopped at Manchester
OL,9,FAirport in May after arriving from Los
OL,10,FAngeles with eight suitcases
OL,11,Fcontaining 158 kilograms of cannabis.
OL,13,FHe was jailed for three years and four
OL,14,Fmonths at Manchester Minshull Street
OL,15,FCrown Court on July 19.
OL,17,FAnother major seizure occurred at
OL,18,FBirmingham Airport on August 9, when
OL,19,F510 kilograms of cannabis was
OL,20,Fdiscovered in 28 suitcases arriving
OL,21,Ffrom Thailand via Paris.
