OL,3,CHuge rise in passengers smuggling
OL,4,Ccannabis in luggage at UK airports
OL,6,FEleven passengers were arrested and
OL,7,Fbailed until November 9.
OL,9,FThis year, about half of those
OL,10,Farrested (184) travelled from
OL,11,FThailand, 75 from Canada, and 47 from
OL,12,Fthe US.
OL,14,FReports suggest couriers are being
OL,15,Fpaid up to #10,000 per trip, but they
OL,16,Fare falsely told they will only face a
OL,17,Ffine if caught.
OL,19,FIn reality, the maximum penalty for
OL,20,Fcannabis importation in the UK is 14
OL,21,Fyears in prison.
