OL,11,FNCA Director General of Threats James
OL,12,FBabbage said: "In some cases, it is
OL,13,Funclear whether the mules knew what
OL,14,Fthe potential penalties are but in
OL,15,Fmost cases, they were operating on
OL,16,Fbehalf of organised criminal gangs.
OL,18,F"And it is those couriers who are
OL,19,Frunning the risk of a potentially life-
OL,20,Fchanging prison sentence.
