OL,4,Ccannabis in luggage at UK airports
OL,6,F"Gangs can make significant profits by
OL,7,Fselling and smuggling perceived high-
OL,8,Fquality cannabis legally grown in the
OL,9,FUSA, Canada and Thailand illegally in
OL,10,Fthe UK.
OL,12,F"We would appeal to anyone who is
OL,13,Fapproached to engage in smuggling to
OL,14,Fthink very carefully about the
OL,15,Fpotential consequences of their
OL,16,Factions, and the risks they will run.
