OL,3,CHuge rise in passengers smuggling
OL,4,Ccannabis in luggage at UK airports
OL,6,F"We know organised criminals can be
OL,7,Fpersuasive, and offer to pay couriers.
OL,8,FBut the risks of getting caught are
OL,9,Fhigh, and it just isn't worth that
OL,10,Frisk."
OL,12,FMinister for Immigration and
OL,13,FCitizenship, Seema Malhotra said:
OL,14,F"Illegal drugs cause harm to
OL,15,Fcommunities and fuel criminal gangs.
OL,16,FWe will not tolerate people attempting
OL,17,Fto bring them into our country.
