OL,6,F"Our Border Force officers are
OL,7,Fcommitted to finding and seizing
OL,8,Fcannabis and other illegal drugs, and
OL,9,Flast year Border Force seized a record
OL,10,Famount of cannabis.
OL,12,F"Anyone caught bringing cannabis to
OL,13,Fthe UK will face the full force of the
OL,14,Flaw, and Border Force will continue to
OL,15,Fwork relentlessly alongside the NCA to
OL,16,Fkeep illegal substances off our
OL,17,Fstreets."
